INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (885,1,'2026-06-23 11:41:25','2026-06-23 11:41:25','<p>Our Smart Mobile LED Poster Screen is a next-generation high-definition digital signage solution designed to maximize advertising impact in high-traffic commercial environments. Built with a lightweight, high-tensile aluminum alloy frame, it combines a sleek, ultra-slim profile with extreme structural durability.</p>\n<h2>Lightweight Aluminum Mobile Design &amp; Easy Setup</h2>\n<p>Featuring a slim 60mm borderless casing, the poster display is exceptionally thin. The base is integrated with heavy-duty lockable rolling caster wheels and a fold-out kickstand, allowing a single person to easily push, park, and deploy the screen without installation. It supports multiple installation options: floor-standing with kickstand, vertical hanging from trusses, wall-mounting, or multi-screen seamless splicing.</p>\n<h2>Smart Cloud Clustering &amp; Content Control</h2>\n<p>The system is powered by an advanced multimedia controller that supports Wi-Fi, 4G, USB playback, and HDMI input. With smart cloud clustering control, marketing managers can update content, schedules, and screen states across multiple poster screens globally through a single centralized dashboard. The plug-and-play USB feature allows offline content loop playback, ensuring zero downtime even without network coverage.</p>\n<h2>Outstanding High-Definition Specifications</h2>\n<p>Equipped with premium P1.5 fine pitch LEDs (422,500 dots/m²) and a high refresh rate of ≥3840Hz, the display guarantees flicker-free visuals under phone cameras and professional studio broadcasting. A brightness level of 800 - 1200 nits ensures clear readability under bright indoor ambient lights, while the wide 160-degree viewing angle attracts audiences from all directions.</p>','Smart Mobile LED Poster Screen P1.5 — High-Definition Indoor Digital Signage','Premium High-Definition Mobile LED Poster Screen P1.5 features an ultra-slim aluminum cabinet (35kg complete unit) with built-in castor wheels and kickstand. Engineered with smart cloud clustering control, USB offline playback, and 1200 nit brightness. The ideal plug-and-play digital signage for retail shops, hotels, exhibitions, and flagship store fronts.','publish','closed','closed','','smart-mobile-led-poster-screen-p15','','','2026-06-23 11:41:25','2026-06-23 11:41:25','',0,'',0,'product','',0);
